 * Shadow Cat nodded to Iron Raptor upon hearing her
words. She began to run to the Ark, hopping over bots,
bushes and anything else in her way, she stopped at
the Ark's door. Then entered. She glanced back, and
seeing Iron in shambles, and Prowl carrying her back
to the base, she almost passed-out herself. She had
not even left her 3 minutes ago and she was already
hurt. She sighed and called Snow Tech on the
com-link.*

 " Yo Bro, Iron's hurt and has ordered us NOT to fire
on the Alliance, so get your skip-plate back to the
Ark so we can re-group and get our stuff, O.K.?"

 * She then waited for Snow Tech to come-back. Hoping
that he was not seriously injured.*
